{"type": "article", "id": 33668, "title": "木搁架变造型，扭一扭就行了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-24T23:07:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 34243, "name": "WeWood"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 168, "image": "img/article/article_show/201610241657037pa1GAwIbNcPdoVU.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>X2 Bookshelf by Laurindo Marta</h3><p>你见过需要扭一扭的搁架吗？Laurindo Marta 为葡萄牙木制家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.wewood.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WeWood</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.wewood.eu/products/bookshelves/x2bookshelf/\" rel=\"nofollow\">X2</a> 就是一款可以自由变化造型的模块化搁架，两个相同尺寸的架子采用了格栅结构，可以灵活地进行伸缩，因此运输起来也相当方便。用户需要做的就是思考所需的样式，再用工具将架子重叠的部分用配件固定起来即可。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024165726HIiaB3GLngd5cPRy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024165726qcO16yBXVTGoHjW3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024165727VeCp0PA8ixsvE4rQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024165726dteP4HNO2vZ0V9fI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.931667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024165727mb8Bnw46rHOKIgEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Bag by Krukru Studio</h3><p>我们曾介绍过莫斯科 MrsChaplinShop 出品的以书为灵感的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31956.html\">手拿包设计</a>，如果你想要一个更特别的包，同样来自莫斯科的 Krukru Studio 会让你体会到“什么都能做成包”是怎样的概念：除了书籍之外，汽车、水果、动物和一些标志性的事物都变成了设计师的创意来源。以羊毛织物为主要材质的 MrsChaplinShop 不同，Krukru Studio 的包既有毛毡款也有皮革款。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/krukrustudio\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>查看它出售的所有系列，希望它不会加重你的选择恐惧症。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501dCc1Bfya6EG9sNUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664912\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501RrHBIaj0P9U8zTFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750877\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501TwXJIrjtRY0ogPzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.891228\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501xa5L6YoF8KfZ0H12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.945000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501fiRuQLblmeow2P6h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830078\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024171501spiKLuBJ40QAqhyU.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.990584\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Anchor cable by Native Union</h3><p>放在桌上的原装充电线总往下滑？配件制作商 <a href=\"http://www.nativeunion.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Native Union</a> 为此推出了这款名叫 Anchor 的充电线，6.5 英尺（约合 1.9 米）的总长是普通 Lightning 充电线的六倍，方便用户在充电时也能自由地使用手机。和之前推出的“毛线球”充电线 <a href=\"http://www.nativeunion.com/night-cable/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Night Cable</a> 相似的是，它同样采用了一个像是船坞一样的固定用配件。不过这次的造型是一个小巧的几何多边体。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.nativeunion.com/anchor-cable/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 34.99 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102417400868XxiQ7sjkcOpfoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024174008M3EmZtd5k7FpfR8P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024174008ra8cHXq5pASte72B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024174008YMH19pGb7uQT5AC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Glissade furniture by Christian Heikoop</h3><p>在荷兰设计周上，今年刚从埃因霍芬设计学院（Design Academy Eindhoven）毕业的 <a href=\"http://christianheikoop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christian Heikoop</a> 带来了这套扁平化家具系列 <a href=\"http://christianheikoop.com/#glissade\" rel=\"nofollow\">Glissade</a>。Heikoop 一直都很喜欢那些以易组装为核心设计的野营设备，在设计 Glissade 时做了不少参考。这些看起来既柔软又坚韧的家具由皮革和金属管构成，完全不需要额外的工具就可以组装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180036CkUqph2Bxc6iAXR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562183\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610241800357HrPKZeABSOn23uc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.409898\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180035gkxDjRG5vd74lUcn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180035lOSv0PNLcbrI82Vu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.788494\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610241800358WiClnqp5Nz1HfQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.054569\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Oxygen vase by Weisi Li</h3><p>          </p><p class=\"\">这些看起来像是字母 O 缺了一个小口的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/40931947/Oxygen-Vase\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oxygen</a> 花瓶是深圳设计师<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/weisili\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">李伟斯</a>的作品。除了花器这一功能之外，与开口对称的一侧还有着数个小洞，在倒水时只要改变方向就变成了一个洒水器。如果你打算循环利用花瓶里的水，这个简单实用的设计就能满足你的需求。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180346ntvL87AsXRpQwe63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180346xeU2mZpFi5hL9JNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.104167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180346yi5hp93jQWlwZvsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610241803461SxQpDfV2RLPUC0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Zen Stone Lights by Neo Nguyen &amp; Clover Pham</h3><p>          </p><p>越南设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/neonguyen\" rel=\"nofollow\">Neo Nguyen</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/cloverpham\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clover Pham</a> 以大自然中的石头为灵感，做了一次颇具禅意的尝试。这个名叫 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43615415/Zen-Stone-Lights-Concept\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zen Stone Light</a> 的灯具概念设计由石头形状的灯罩和底部的 LED 线路板组成，在完成 3D 打印后两位设计师在每块“石头”上手工喷洒了颜色，这也使得每个灯具因此有了独一无二的斑纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180531HR4snbeMNkLydahP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180531txR2na0N9BKS8Jp4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180531lBOztihKnm3Pe0ua.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610241805316oGw7V9QCHrMyjfs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.370714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161024180531EnuBgb2ZLkIdPDqO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}